  description = 'Perform Landmine Handle-Grip Deadlift as a landmine-based hinge pattern. The athlete uses the fixed angled bar path to create useful load while maintaining bracing, breathing, grip ownership, and a repeatable finish position.',
  card_summary = 'Landmine Handle-Grip Deadlift is a landmine exercise for handle-grip landmine deadlift for hips, trunk, and grip with easy setup and exit. Use it when the goal is quality force, posture, and repeatable bar path rather than fatigue chasing.',
